	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">Mountains and Craters are impenetrable: they totally bar visibility of what's beyond for everything (except for flying units).<br />Forests, mountains and hills are all "blocking" terrain. Units can see into such tiles, but they cannot see past them - unless they occupy a hill. Units in hills can see over blocking terrain into the tiles beyond.</div>
